Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.37,0:01:35.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen,\ngood evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:39.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There are men who sniff around the mystery\nthat surrounds myself and my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:43.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Little by little, their search brings\nthem closer to our secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.68,0:01:49.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hear me, young man and young lady.\NHear me, noble souls acting in unison.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:51.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Be on your guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.62,0:01:55.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and know that there are some things in\nthis world that one is better off not knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:57.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:09.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You miserable brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:11.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:16.03,count fo,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,350)}Act 14:\NLost Souls
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:22.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You sons of...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:30.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count! Are you\nall right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:32.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You needn't worry\nabout me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.56,0:02:34.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:44.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this\nhappening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.17,0:02:47.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't my record\nalways been perfect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:50.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You should know that!\NRight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:53.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been above reproach,\nwith no blemish on my record!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:56.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:03:01.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is all your fault! It's all because\nyou brought that accursed Count to Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:05.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What lies did you fill his head with?!\NTell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.19,0:03:09.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mark my words! Don't get cocky!\NYou'll be next!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.80,0:03:14.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Disaster will come calling\nat your house, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:15.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Give it a rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:16.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:21.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea who I am?!\NLet go! Get your hands off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:22.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.14,0:03:25.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You should\ngo home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:28.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let us meet again\nsome other time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:31.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:40.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:42.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ali!\NDo your thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:05.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your abilities are as\nimpressive as ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:10.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert! This is all\nyour fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:15.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be next! Disaster will come\ncalling at your house, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:22.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've been in there for ages.\NDid something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine.\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:26.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maximilien is here\nto see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:30.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maximilien!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:42.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:44.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to\nsee you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:45.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why the sudden\nreturn to Paris?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.49,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've come here to fetch\NMonsieur Noirtier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:52.40,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that he should be\nat Valentine's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:59.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I came here expecting to have another\nquarrel with Monsieur Villefort,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:03.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but I heard the news of his arrest\nthe instant I arrived in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:07.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It came as quite a shock to hear\nwhat had become of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:08.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:14.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to come pay you a visit\nand express my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:17.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for all you\nhave done for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:20.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Still as upright and formal\nas ever, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was because you were\nthere for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:27.23,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that I was able to save those\nwho are dearest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:30.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing else, please don't\nforget that one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:32.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maximilien...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:37.24,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am glad that\NI met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:41.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care\nof Valentine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:43.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:50.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See you around,\NMaximilien.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:58.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, my stocks have hit the\ntrading limit for several days in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:01.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,These various tidbits of information\nfind their way to me, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:03.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really ask\nfor them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:05.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how I envy you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:10.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's a waste of one's life to tie one's happiness\nto the fluctuations of numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:12.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:17.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Dramatic Arrest of Crown Prosecutor\NVillefort in Public Spectacle."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:19.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is most shocking,\nisn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:22.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One never can tell what will\nhappen next in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:29.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Baron, what's this I hear about you\nand the Crown Prosecutor being old friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:32.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all, not at all! We're just acquaintances,\nwe're not what you'd call friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:40.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that true? You, General Morcerf, and\nthe Crown Prosecutor here are old friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.74,0:06:44.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and you've used each other's influence\nto expand your own power bases.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:48.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard stories along those lines,\nso I was curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:51.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,T-That must be a rumor spread\nby jealous people, no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:54.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:59.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Still, people can be brought low\nby the most unexpected things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:04.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest that you exercise the utmost caution\nin the company you choose to keep, Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:10.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Baron?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.87,0:07:11.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:15.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite serious about\nyour daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:21.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to receive your blessing\nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:34.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a mess...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:46.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to keep you waiting.\NMy name is Beauchamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're a reporter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:50.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:53.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then this is\nyour lucky day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:57.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna have a scoop that's gonna\nbe splashed across the front page!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:07:58.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want\nin return?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:04.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How much will your company\npay for a big scoop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:06.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really busy, so if\nyou'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:12.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! I'm talkin' about a huge scandal\ninvolving General Morcerf!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:16.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is gonna knock\neven YOUR socks off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:28.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:29.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you need to\nsee me so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:33.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're doing a special feature on\NGeneral Morcerf's presidential bid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:38.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I should use my personal connections,\nso I was hoping to ask you a few questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:40.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, if it's something\NI can answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:41.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:51.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why do you think your father\nhas managed to achieve such success?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:56.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to hear your frank opinion\nas one of the people closest to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:59.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:02.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it would be\nhis sincerity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:07.39,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My father loves and worries about the country in\nthe same way that he loves my mother deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.02,0:09:10.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard about how\nmy father became a hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:13.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...by defending Janina's citadel\nto the bitter end?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:17.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After he returned to Paris, he used that as\na springboard and shot up through the ranks,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:20.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...even making it to the rank of general\nin spite of his young age.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:25.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And now he's making a bid\nfor the presidency, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:29.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. My father's enthusiasm for\npolitics is the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:30.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:33.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rooting for\nyour father, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:37.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's times like these when a man makes a lot\nof enemies. You should watch your back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:39.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:47.49,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But when you deal in gossip like you do in my\nline of work, you get all kinds of crazy tips.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.03,0:09:52.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Tales of bribery, kickbacks, illicit affairs...\NYou get sick of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:58.23,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's hilarious! My father isn't\ninvolved with any of that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:03.24,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, I'm more worried that he might be\na little too straight-laced to be a politician.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:04.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:08.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be relieved if he ever\ndid something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:11.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"He's a lot more shrewd\nthan I gave him credit for."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:14.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess you're right.\NSorry to worry you over nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:18.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The fact of the matter is, a fishy guy\npaid me a visit today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:23.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He was this creepy, sleazy old man.\NWhat did he say his name was?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:26.39,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Caderousse," or something\nlike that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:29.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What did he...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:31.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What did that man say\nabout my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:34.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, some stupid story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:39.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something about how the stories of your\nfather's exploits at Janina are all a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:41.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I told him he was full of crap\nand chased him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:44.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.59,0:10:49.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Open flames are strictly prohibited\nin this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.69,0:10:52.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please extinguish your\nlighter immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:55.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Smoking is prohibited\nin this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.06,0:10:57.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please smoke only in\ndesignated areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:07.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'd better\nlook into this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:21.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Step right up! Pay our establishment\na visit tonight, my good gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.86,0:11:27.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The dead man has\ncome back to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:32.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Edmond would never forget what we did,\nnot in a million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:35.36,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something about how the stories of your\nfather's exploits at Janina are all a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:38.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Disaster will come calling\nat your house, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:42.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not possible. It couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.10,count alt,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for agreeing to speak with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:45.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,First of all,\NMarquis Cavalcanti,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:49.51,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...there has been an announcement that you are\nmaking a huge investment in the Danglars Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:51.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What was it that made you decide\non that particular bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:55.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I leave all investment matters\nto my advisory analysts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:59.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I abide by their decisions and follow\ntheir advice. That is the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:04.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There are also rumors that you have been\nseeing Baron Danglars' daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.40,0:12:06.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:10.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I realize that it is a personal question,\nbut if you would care to make a comment...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:12.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, just a\nbrief one, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:18.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The fact is, Eugenie de Danglars and I\nwere formally engaged this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:21.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My goodness!\NIt's like a fairy tale!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:24.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?\NCongratulations on your engagement!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:26.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is big news, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:29.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He has to be lying...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:34.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot. If I'd known you were here,\NI would've been able to play even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:36.36,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I would've been playing\nfor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:39.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Naturally, she's overjoyed\nabout this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:40.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Step right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:42.23,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:47.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eugenie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:53.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I have to speak with Eugenie.\NLet me see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:57.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mademoiselle has said that she\ndoesn't wish to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:13:00.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see her in person and\nask her how she feels about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:03.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry, Monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:09.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please! At least tell her\nthat I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:13.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eugenie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:24.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Was someone at the door\njust now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.28,0:13:28.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mademoiselle.\NJust a deliveryman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.57,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.65,0:13:35.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are all these\nflowers for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:38.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning\nof this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:42.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How could you arrange an engagement\nfor me without asking me about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:47.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that your happiness\nis my main concern, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:49.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I'M the one who's going\nto have to marry him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:51.23,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:55.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's too soon for you to make\nimportant decisions on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:58.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really mean what\nyou're saying, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:00.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:03.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you'd stop\ndoing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:09.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going? I invited\NMarquis Cavalcanti to dinner tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:11.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:17.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for Albert,\nhe's out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:19.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Out where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:20.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:21.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:32.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:24.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! I didn't throw mine\nthat hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!\NJerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:29.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're gonna\nget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:36.57,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over between\nme and Eugenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:39.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that she got engaged\nto Cavalcanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.14,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:46.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't what Eugenie wants.\NThere's something behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:50.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you know Eugenie would never\nvoluntarily get engaged to a guy like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.82,0:15:53.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not so sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:55.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:59.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell what's true,\nand what's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:03.23,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:04.17,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:07.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz... I'm still me,\naren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:12.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens,\NI'll still be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:17.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Franz, tell me!\NI won't change, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:20.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens,\NI'm still gonna be me, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.69,0:16:34.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Death is certain, its hour uncertain," huh?\NTalk about a sinister expression...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:38.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:42.23,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As far as I'm concerned,\NI think I'd rather know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:46.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even if learning the truth\nchanged who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:48.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Franz...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:51.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of leaving\NParis for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:54.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're going back\nto Luna or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:58.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea! At a time\nlike this, a trip is the best thing to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:00.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I can't\ntake you with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:05.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell not?!\NWhat's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.06,0:17:07.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:11.23,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:15.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now I get it.\NWe've all grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:17.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to keep secrets\nfrom each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:23.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You and I should call\nit quits, too, Franz.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:29.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, a secret hideout?\NWhat are we, kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:31.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:49.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Albert.\NTrust me, I'll get to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:00.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:03.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:08.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am right\nas rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:13.59,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?\NYou're out without an umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:17.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I thought that getting soaked for a change\nwouldn't be such a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.37,0:18:23.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, I'm on my way\nto go off into space again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:26.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?\NWould you care to join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:30.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Today isn't\na good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:31.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:32.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:39.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there is no need to apologize. I hope that\nyou will accept my offer some other time, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:58.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot bring myself to leave you here;\nnot with that look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:02.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come, let us go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:09.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:13.29,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We waited for you,\nbut dinner has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:15.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was out looking\nfor Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:20.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see that there is still room in\nyour heart for no one but him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:24.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur Albert has gone off\ninto deep space.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:29.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, he is going to spend time\nwith the Count at his summer retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:32.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... He is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:37.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. There's been a steady\nstream of flowers to congratulate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:43.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This one is from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:03.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why do these things\nkeep happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:08.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you suppose\nthat is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:13.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count, I'm afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:17.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the truth?\NWhat is a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:19.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That is something that you\nmust decide for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.76,0:20:25.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have the resolve to overcome\nyour limitations and press ever onward?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:31.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you possess a powerful will that bends\nto no one, I can say this with certainty:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:35.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You will be\nall right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:37.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:52.39,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The first public speech by presidential race\nforerunner General Fernand de Morcerf...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:55.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...is about to begin in the\NNational Assembly building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.99,0:20:58.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Numerous public figures have also\nrushed here to show their support,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:01.56,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and the crowd inside the hall\nis already at a fever pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,General Morcerf,\nit's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.37,0:21:06.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please take your place\non the stage, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:10.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I only made it this far because\NI had you at my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:14.57,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.57,0:21:40.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get the car ready!\NI'm going to the National Assembly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.60,0:23:13.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Away from the worlds of men,\NI find myself alone with the Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.60,0:23:15.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But there is no escaping\nfrom the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.40,0:23:19.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Gankutsuou,\NThe Count of Monte Cristo act 15:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.04,0:23:21.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,..."The End of Happiness,\NThe Beginning of Truth."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:21.08,count fo,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,350)}Act 15:\NThe End of Happiness, The Beginning of Truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.94,0:23:24.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bide your time,\nand hold out hope!
